The idea is of https://twitter.com/arturo182 and Philippe Cadic

The base of the board is Philippe Cadic's https://github.com/ccadic/Q10OLED

Keypad library for GPIO extender (base of Keypad_PCA955X) is Joe Young's https://github.com/joeyoung/arduino_keypads

USB-C footprint is https://github.com/arturo182/GT-USB-7010 (LCSC.com carries this, search for USB Type C 16p)

LoRa module RFM95 and ESP-WROOM-32 KiCad from github.com/automote